high_descs: Turn and go to the table.
Pick up the butter knife on the table.
Turn and go to the shelves in the corner.
Cut the apple on the shelves.
Turn and go to the table by the stove.
Put the butter knife on the table.
Turn and go to the shelves in the corner.
Pick up a slice of apple on the shelves.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Heat the slice of apple in the microwave.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Put the slice of apple on the table by the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of apple by the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the table
Pick up the knife on the table
Turn right, go forward, turn right and go to the shelf unit
Cut the apple on the shelf unit
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn right
Put the knife on the table
Turn right, go forward
Pick up a piece of apple
Turn around, go forward, turn left, go forward, turn right, go forward, turn left in front of the microwave
Put the apple piece in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the apple piece from the microwave
Turn down to the table under the microwave
Put the apple piece on the table
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple, cook a piece of it

high_descs: Turn around and go straight to the table behind you.
Pick up the knife that is in front of the fork on the left side of the table.
With the knife in your hand turn and go to the little brown shelf to the left of the sink.
Slice the apple in three parts that is in the front of the other apples and to the right of the spoon.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the table the toaster is on.
Place the knife on the far right side of the table to the left of the yellow and silver object.
Turn to your right to face the little brown shelf that the apples are on.
Pick a slice up of the apple that is to the left of the spoon.  Get the slice closest to you.
With the slice of apple in hand go to the table the microwave is on.
Open the microwave and place the apple in on the right side.  Close the door and start the microwave.  When done open the door and grab the apple slice.
Move down slightly so you are looking at the table.
Place the apple slice behind that bottle of lotion that is on the table to your left.
anns.task_desc: Slice an apple to warm up and place on table.
